('ONET-RAIL_TRANSPORTATION_WORKERS_ALL_OTHER', 'source_onet_rail_transportation_workers_all_other', 'Rail Transportation Workers, All Other', 'Rail Transportation Workers, All Other is an imported ONET role/occupation concept. It needs TALLENTIN normalization before production routing.', 'role_title', 'All rail transportation workers not listed separately.', ARRAY['Ballast Cleaning Operator','Ballast Regulator Operator','Block Operator','Car Barn Laborer','Car Retarder Operator','Control Tower Operator','Hostler Helper','Hot Box Checker','Hot Box Spotter','Interlocker','Interlocking Tower Operator','Lever Operator','Oiler Helper','Power Ballast Machine Operator','Rail Tractor Operator','Rail Transportation Tabeler','Rail Walker','Railroad Hand','Railroad Worker','Railroader','Railway Equipment Operator','Retarder Operator','Semaphore Operator','Signal Operator','Signal Tower Director','Signal Tower Operator','Tableman','Tamping Machine Operator','Target Man','Target Worker','Tower Director','Tower Observer','Tower Operator','Tower Switch Operator','Tower Watchman','Towerman','Track Broom Operator','Trackmobile Operator','Train Director','Transfer Table Operator','Transfer Table Operator Helper','Turntable Engineer']::text[], ARRAY['Rail Transportation Workers, All Other','Ballast Cleaning Operator','Ballast Regulator Operator','Block Operator','Car Barn Laborer','Car Retarder Operator','Control Tower Operator','Hostler Helper','Hot Box Checker','Hot Box Spotter','Interlocker','Interlocking Tower Operator','Lever Operator','Oiler Helper','Power Ballast Machine Operator','Rail Tractor Operator','Rail Transportation Tabeler','Rail Walker','Railroad Hand','Railroad Worker','Railroader','Railway Equipment Operator','Retarder Operator','Semaphore Operator','Signal Operator','Signal Tower Director']::text[], ARRAY[]::text[], '{"source_imported_skills":[]}'::jsonb, '["approved_capability","industry_context","employment_model"]'::jsonb, '["source_imported_role","skills","tas